data.description: Move-in ready Spokane Valley Rancher on a 1/4 acre corner lot in the Central Valley School District. The primary suite includes a full bathroom, double sinks, and a walk-in closet. The kitchen was remodeled in 2020 with laminate counters and stainless steel appliances, as well as new flooring in the bedrooms and bathrooms, and main floor utilities. Attached garage, off-street, and RV parking. Would make a great owner occupy or rental.
